Text: New Jersey Natural GasEnron ISDACSA Cc Enron ISDA doc There has been some confusion on this ISDACSA since originally there was no electronic version I have tried to incorporate all comments into this electronic document Please make all written comments directly on this document If you prefer you may call me to discuss comments at There are no comments on the Guaranty I have received two different guaranty versions from Enron In my last phone conversation with Darren Vanek on Darren indicated he was going to talk to Stephanie about providing one guaranty for both financial and physical transactions Regards Adrienne Kalbacher Contracts Manager Enron ISDA doc

RE Enron Corp Guaranty Cc Stephanie Attached are NJNGs comments on your guaranty Please review and let me know if these changes are acceptable Please note the guaranty references the ISDA I submitted comments to you on for an ISDACSA between our companies Would you please give me the status of this review Thank you Adrienne Kalbacher Contracts Manager Original Message From Panus Stephanie mailto Sent Friday October PM To Subject Enron Corp Guaranty Adrienne Attached for your review is the form of Enron Corp Guaranty covering ENA in both physical and financial transactions with New Jersey Natural Gas nj nat gasdraftdoc Stephanie Panus Senior Legal Specialist Enron Wholesale Services Smith Street EBC Houston Texas ph fax email This email is the property of Enron Corp andor its relevant affiliate and may contain confidential and privileged material for the sole use of the intended recipient s Any review use distribution or disclosure by others is strictly prohibited If you are not the intended recipient or authorized to receive for the recipient please contact the sender or reply to Enron Corp at and delete all copies of the message This email and any attachments hereto are not intended to be an offer or an acceptance and do not create or evidence a binding and enforceable contract between Enron Corp or any of its affiliates and the intended recipient or any other party and may not be relied on by anyone as the basis of a contract by estoppel or otherwise Thank you Enron guaranty to NJNG doc
